video:video.video:title: Dr. Martens Individual Style United Spirit
video:video.video:description:
Dr. Martens Autumn 2012 featuring Alice Dellal.
Tribes are about bonds. These bonds are not just strengthened by style but by substance. A shared spirit, an attitude, an instinct. For many, their first pair of Dr Martens is both a statement of self expression and a stamp of belonging.

video:video.video:title: Dr. Martens X Agyness Deyn AW13
video:video.video:description:
Agyness Deyn perfectly embodies the Dr. Martens ethos of standing for something, with her very British desire for creative self-expression.
The inspiration for her third collection comes from the subcultural heritage of Dr. Martens, and her own interpretation of the Mod 'look'.
The range will be available to buy from Dr. Martens own retail stores globally from September 2013.
Music by Brown Brogues "Mike I Love You" https://soundcloud.com/brownbrogues
